        <mxCell id="pc_legend_text" value="Every task passes two review gates: approval to &lt;b&gt;start&lt;/b&gt; and approval to &lt;b&gt;finish&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;No single person can both propose and complete a task without oversight." style="text;html=1;fontSize=9;fontColor=#495057;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" parent="1" vertex="1">
